Package org.eclipse.jetty.util.thread

Interface ThreadPool.SizedThreadPool

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.concurrent.Executor, ThreadPool
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExecutorSizedThreadPool, ExecutorThreadPool, MonitoredQueuedThreadPool, QueuedThreadPool
    Enclosing interface:
    ThreadPool
    public static interface ThreadPool.SizedThreadPool
extends ThreadPool

    Specialized sub-interface of ThreadPool that allows to get/set the minimum and maximum number of threads of the pool.
